      "text": "Honestly: The Infamous Andrew Schulz",
      "url": "https://www.commonsense.news/p/honestly-the-infamous-andrew-schulz"
    },
    {
      "text": "There\u2019s a tried-and-true playbook for comedians who want to make it big: hit the road, get in front of as many audiences as possible, and try to grab the attention of the TV executives who decide which comics are lucky enough to get a special. But Andrew Schulz and his generation\u2026",
